---
title: Easy American Pulled Beef Loaded Fries with Sour Cream Slaw & Cheesy Crisps
description: Kind of like nachos, but with a brand new personality, these loaded fries are the ultimate comfort food. Pile them high with saucy
pulled beef, then serve with cheesy Parmesan crisps and a creamy slaw. Now, get cosy and tuck in!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*Our pulled beef is gently
cooked while vacuum-sealed
(or 'sous vide' as the French
say). The meat may look pale,
but it's packed with flavour
and moisture!*
